      "value": "<p><strong>Level 2</strong> Transmutation</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 bonus</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> undefined self</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Concentration, up to 1 minute</p>\n\nThe target hit by the strike takes an extra 2d6 Radiant damage from the attack. Until the spell ends, the target sheds Bright Light|XPHB in a 5-foot radius, attack rolls against it have Advantage|XPHB, and it can't benefit from the Invisible|XPHB condition.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> The damage increases by 2d6|2-9|1d6 for each spell slot level above 2.</p>",
